%% Best-Fee Mode Full Sequence Diagram
%% Shows the 4-phase flow: broadcast, candidate collection,
%% selection (via expiration cascade), and delivery.

sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant A0 as A0 (Originator)
    participant A1 as A1 (Relay 1)
    participant A3 as A3 (Relay 2)
    participant A6 as A6 (Relay 3 - Leaf)
    participant A8 as A8 (Recipient)
    participant Cleanup as CleanupService

    Note over User,A8: Phase 1 — Request Broadcasting (fast=0, hopWait=15s)

    User->>A0: eiou send A8 5 USD --best
    A0->>A0: Set expiration=T+60, hopWait=15
    A0->>A1: P2P(hash, fast=0, hopWait=15, exp=T+60)
    A1->>A1: Cap exp: min(scaled, T+60-15) = T+45
    A1->>A3: P2P(hash, fast=0, hopWait=15, exp=T+45)
    A3->>A3: Cap exp: min(scaled, T+45-15) = T+30
    A3->>A6: P2P(hash, fast=0, hopWait=15, exp=T+30)
    A6->>A6: Cap exp: min(scaled, T+30-15) = T+15
    A6->>A8: P2P(hash, fast=0, hopWait=15, exp=T+15)

    Note over User,A8: Phase 2 — Candidate Collection

    A8->>A6: RP2P(hash, amount=5.03, fee=0.03)
    A6->>A6: Store in rp2p_candidates
    Note right of A6: Other paths may also<br/>deliver RP2P candidates

    Note over User,A8: Phase 3 — Cascading Selection (leaf-to-root)

    Cleanup->>A6: processCleanupMessages() [T+15]
    A6->>A6: Expired! selectAndForwardBestRp2p()
    A6->>A6: Status → 'found' (prevents re-processing)
    A6->>A3: RP2P(hash, best candidate)
    A3->>A3: Store in rp2p_candidates

    Cleanup->>A3: processCleanupMessages() [T+30]
    A3->>A3: Expired! selectAndForwardBestRp2p()
    A3->>A3: Status → 'found'
    A3->>A1: RP2P(hash, best candidate)
    A1->>A1: Store in rp2p_candidates

    Cleanup->>A1: processCleanupMessages() [T+45]
    A1->>A1: Expired! selectAndForwardBestRp2p()
    A1->>A1: Status → 'found'
    A1->>A0: RP2P(hash, best candidate)
    A0->>A0: Store in rp2p_candidates

    Cleanup->>A0: processCleanupMessages() [T+60]
    A0->>A0: Expired! selectAndForwardBestRp2p()
    A0->>A0: Status → 'found'

    Note over User,A8: Phase 4 — Transaction Delivery (along best route)

    A0->>A1: Transaction (5 USD + fees)
    A1->>A3: Transaction (forwarded)
    A3->>A6: Transaction (forwarded)
    A6->>A8: Transaction (delivered)
    A8->>A8: Balance updated
